name: Fortyfour_oilpainting_V1
description:
此模型可以产出一些古典主义派系油画，需要油画笔触更加明显可以将CFG降低至2-3，在prompt加入oilpainting：1.5.脸部或细节处可以考虑inpating高降噪重绘产出.tile效果极佳.

高CFG也可以产生出一些真实系人物，肌理比较细腻

在线跑图可以用Fortyfour_oilpainting_1557 - oilpaint | 吐司 Tusi.Art

This model can produce some oil paintings of Classicism factions, and the CFG can be reduced to 2-3 if the oil painting strokes are more obvious. Adding oilpainting in prompt: 1.5. High noise reduction repaint of inpating can be considered at the face or details to produce excellent. tile effect

High CFG can also produce some realistic characters with delicate textures
